<img src="http://biz-file.com/c/1805/440227.jpg" alt="Howard Audio: In the swing of things - with SAMA-nominated album by Swing City" width="400" height="388">Swing City (Loyiso Bala, Graeme Watkins and Nathan Ro) have recorded and mixed both of their albums at Howard Audio. Their latest nominated album is called Now Listen Properly -  consisting of 12 tracks including six famous South African songs, all given a contemporary swing feel by musical director and arranger David Cousins and featuring some of South Africa’s most illustrious musicians. <img src="http://biz-file.com/c/1805/440228.jpg" alt="Howard Audio: In the swing of things - with SAMA-nominated album by Swing City" width="400" height="300"><img src="http://biz-file.com/c/1805/440229.jpg" alt="Howard Audio: In the swing of things - with SAMA-nominated album by Swing City" width="400" height="355"><img src="http://biz-file.com/c/1805/440230.jpg" alt="Howard Audio: In the swing of things - with SAMA-nominated album by Swing City" width="400" height="300">Now Listen Properly was recorded over a three-week period, using Howard Audio’s state-of-the-art analogue hardware. <img src="http://biz-file.com/c/1805/440231.jpg" alt="Howard Audio: In the swing of things - with SAMA-nominated album by Swing City" width="400" height="533">We’re proud and humbled to have been part of the process.<img src="http://biz-file.com/c/1805/440232.jpg" alt="Howard Audio: In the swing of things - with SAMA-nominated album by Swing City" width="400" height="400">Good luck to all the nominees.